# 📝 To-Do List Application

🚀 Developed during my remote frontend web development internship with OctaNet Services Pvt. Ltd., this sophisticated To-Do list application leverages HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to provide a seamless user experience.

## Features

- *Task Categorization:* Organize your tasks into General, Work, and Personal categories. 📂
- *Date Assignment:* Assign due dates to tasks for better time management. 📅
- *Task Management:* Mark tasks as complete or delete them as needed. ✅❌

## Technologies Used

- *HTML*: Structuring the web content. 🌐
- *CSS*: Styling the application. 🎨
- *JavaScript*: Adding interactivity and functionality. 💻

